description: Returns attributes for one or more VPC endpoints associated with the current account. For more information, see Access Amazon OpenSearch Serverless using an interface endpoint.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the specified VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: vpcId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC from which you access OpenSearch Serverless.

nested_items.name: subnetIds
nested_items.description: The ID of the subnets from which you access OpenSearch Serverless.

nested_items.name: securityGroupIds
nested_items.description: The unique identifiers of the security groups that define the ports, protocols, and sources for inbound traffic that you are authorizing into your endpoint.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current status of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: createdDate
nested_items.description: The date the endpoint was created.

nested_items.name: failureCode
nested_items.description: A failure code associated with the request.

nested_items.name: failureMessage
nested_items.description: A message associated with the failure code.

nested_items.name: vpcEndpointErrorDetails
nested_items.description: Error information for a failed request.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: An error message describing the reason for the failure.

nested_items.name: errorCode
nested_items.description: The error code for the failed request.
